name: Akame ga Kill! Ultimate Girl Pack
description:
Requests have been put on hold.

Here are some of your top gals from Akame ga Kill!

Use for the character pack

Weight: 1.0

Characters:

  • Akame: akame \(akame ga kill!\), black collared shirt, red necktie, sleeveless, skirt (add black hair and red eyes if necessary)

  • Chelsea: chelsea \(akame ga kill!\), headphones, black vest, white shirt, neck ribbon, long sleeves, plaid skirt

  • Esdeath: esdeath, long blue hair, white peaked cap, blue eyes, white military uniform, long sleeves, white thighhighs, choker, cleavage, large breasts

  • Kurome: kurome, black serafuku, black skirt, pantyhose (add black hair and black eyes if necessary)

  • Leone: leone, blonde hair, cat ears, strapless, detached sleeves, boots, scarf, belt, tail, midriff, large breasts

  • Mine: mine \(akame ga kill!\), long pink hair, twintails, pink dress, ribbon, capelet, pantyhose

  • Sheele: sheele, purple hair, purple eyes, glasses, purple dress, clothing cutout, cleavage cutout, detached sleeves

Surprise! Didn't expect me to come back so soon, did ya'? Well me neither, I just got some stuff done sooner than I thought. I won't be spamming model releases like I usually do, though. I'll be learning the ropes on baking a LoRA on a locally installed instance.

Anyway, in this model, Esdeath is now the most jankiest character to get consistent results, just a warning. Other characters can get messy too if you don't specify their exact appearance.

Use for each individual characters

Weight: 0.8

Characters:

  • Akame's Trigger + Outfit: akame \(akame ga kill!\), black collared shirt, red necktie, sleeveless, skirt

  • Esdeath's Trigger + Appearance + Outfit: esdeath, long blue hair, white peaked cap, blue eyes, white military uniform, white thighhighs, white footwear, thigh boots, choker, cleavage, large breasts

  • Mine's Trigger + Appearance + Outfit: mine \(akame ga kill!\), twintails, dress, ribbon, capelet, black pantyhose

  • Leone's Trigger + Appearance + Outfit: leone, blonde hair, strapless, detached sleeves, boots, scarf, belt, midriff, large breasts

  • Chelsea's Trigger + Outfit: chelsea \(akame ga kill!\), headphones, black vest, white shirt, neck ribbon, long sleeves, plaid skirt

Notes:

  • Akame's hair may occasionally get put in some hairstyles like a ponytail.

  • You may put twintails as a negative prompt if you just want long hair for Mine.

  • Leone has the most funkiest LoRA so far, but she's got her outfit and her animal ears are optional to add (I accidentally pruned them, so I redid the training).

  • Chelsea might decide to put another butterfly ribbon on her headphones. I'd ask her why, but it is what it is.

  • Esdeath's symbol imprinted on her chest isn't perfect but it's there.

Anyways, I think that's all for now. Maybe let me know which one's your favorite? I might consider adding more, but their number of images start to dwindle a little bit, so that'll have to wait. Alright, enjoy!
